imageAssets.description: A sleek, modern, abstract logo for 'Imaginarium AI'. The design should feature subtle, flowing lines or shapes that evoke creativity and artificial intelligence. Use a dark background with primary accent colors of #BB86FC (purple) and secondary accent colors of #03DAC6 (teal). The style should be minimalist and professional, suitable for a technology company. No text in the image, just a symbolic icon.
imageAssets.purpose: Main logo for the website, used in the navbar and potentially footer. Should be small and iconic.

imageAssets.description: A subtle, dark, abstract background image with a gentle gradient or very faint, flowing lines. The colors should primarily be dark grays and blacks, with very subtle hints of #BB86FC (purple) and #03DAC6 (teal) to match the dark theme. It should be non-distracting and suitable for a hero section background or general page background.
